text: Last week included four days of training for NEEMO, then a trip to Huntsville for a briefing and lunch with the STRATCOM and SMDC Commanders
Great day in Huntsville w Kimbrough and community leaders learning about SMDC/ARSTRAT.  Nice to meet new folks and visit with old friends.
19:00 shown during the Olympics.  Must see for space fans about history, competition, achievement, and friendship. http://t.co/coAYF9Ptj6
Heard the phrase, "Measure twice, cut once?" The Russian language version is "Measure seven times,cut once."  Интересно.
Space station food sampling.  The curry flavor in the spicy green beans was so good I asked to finish the leftovers! http://t.co/JQkYv1iqG6
3rd day of lunches sampling space station food today.  Most of it is great!
Eight hours of meetings, admin, and Russian today.  Not a bad office day, especially since one meeting was on a 9-day undersea trip in July.
Finishing a sim with the flight control team prepping for Cygnus 2's berthing with the ISS.  Enjoyed watching @astro_reid arrive last night!
